title: Hour 2 - Jason Hehir (04-17-20)
itunes:title: Hour 2 - Jason Hehir (04-17-20)
description:
With Jalen Green choosing to skip college basketball, is this the end of superstar players in college? Surrounding questions with his injury past, might Tua Tagovailoa slip in the draft? Finally, The Last Dance director Jason Hehir stops by to talk about the film.
